#ROOMS
#30900
Welcome to Room 1~
You are inside but you feel a little like you're going to die.  Wonder if it has
something to do with the strange gas pouring into the room?  Extra flags are
none, extra description on "flag" and rspec is spec_gas_chamber.  Proceed north
if you're close to death.  Oh and only if you want to crack your noggin.
~
