Another Room Code Name 2~
To the south there is a stinky smell, you might not want to go there. East and
down seem like safe smelling options though!  This spot you're standing in now
appears to be a desert its also feeling rather safe!  Exits are south, down
and east.  Oh.. though you can only go back south if you're a mudschool newbie!
