#30904
Resting Spot~
A a lovely peaceful resting spot.  Be nice to stay a while but .. oh crap!  Its
no spell along with being peaceful!  Oh well.  Climb the bank north if you want
but you can't go back west, those silly rapids are there anyway.  Since you're
sitting here there are some descriptions to read like "flower" or "footprints".
There is also a e/w tide.
